ilog.cplex

Class IloCplex.CutType

  • java.lang.Object
    • ilog.cplex.IloCplex.CutType
  • Enclosing class:
    IloCplex

    public static class IloCplex.CutType
extends java.lang.Object
    Enumeration of cut types.

    Cut types can be used with the method IloCplex.getNcuts to query the cuts in use at the end of the previous mixed integer optimization.
